These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, monopoly, domino
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. the person playing canasta is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing mah-jongg##7
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Game   | monopoly | domino       | canasta | mah-jongg        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
City: san-francisco, hannover, paris, hamburg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person traveling to paris##7
2. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
3. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| City     | paris | hannover       | hamburg         | san-francisco     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, bird, horse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, house, indie
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##7
3. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of indie and the owner of the ferret##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | ferret | horse | bird | fish  |
| Music-Genre   | house | classical  | indie   | dubstep |

