.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, hot-chocolate, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person drinking cola##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade | cola       | hot-chocolate |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

