.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, ship, roller
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person driving the skateboard##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport         | ship | skateboard   | roller | trike |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

