.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, ship, car, scooter
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the car is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
6. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the ship##7
7. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Transport   | skateboard    | scooter | ship   | car |

