.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
House: palace, craftsman, modern, futuristic
1. the palace house is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the futuristic house is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| House   | palace | modern | futuristic    | craftsman |

