.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, scientist, security-guard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, ritmeester, blend
1. the engineer is not the tiparillo-smoker##6
2. the scientist is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
5. the scientist is somewhere between the blend-smoker and the police-officer##7
6. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| Cigar   | blend         | ritmeester      | tiparillo | aristoff            |

