.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
House: palace, ranch-style, gothic-revival, victorian
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the victorian house##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the gothic-revival house##6
3. the ranch-style house is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
5. the person watching family movies is the palace house##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| House           | palace    | ranch-style   | victorian  | gothic-revival      |

