.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, frog, dog
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the mouse and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of rock and the owner of the mouse##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Pet   | dog | pony | mouse | frog   |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | soul      | gospel      | trance |

