4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person watching superhero movies##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
