2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the cape-cod house is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
6. the art-deco house is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
