.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, july, february
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Birthday   | july | february  | october | april |

 